title: Stop Dems Before It's Too Late
description: Fellas discuss the latest election news around the map before talking about one brave American's fight with a Grizzly Bear. Tudor Dixon joins the progrum for an interview on her race for Governor of Michigan. Jason Dudash talks about his work with the Freedom Foundation.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Jason Dudash, Tudor Dixon, Michael Duncan, Comfortably Smug, John Ashbrook)
